com.crawljax.core.plugin
Interface GeneratesOutput

All Superinterfaces:
Plugin
All Known Implementing Classes:
SaveCrawlSession
public interface GeneratesOutput
extends Plugin

Interface that adds a setOutputFolder and getOutputFolder method to allow the user to set the directory this plugin should use for its output. Note that the output path should be used as an absolute path.
